13 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 372, O.S.L.
14 2023 (27A O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 3-8-101), is amended to read as
15 follows:
16 Section 3-8-101. This act shall be known and may be cited as
17 the “Terry Peach North Canadian Watershed Water Restoration Act”.
18 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY Section 2, Chapter 372, O.S.L.
19 2023 (27A O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 3-8-102), is amended to read as
20 follows:
21 Section 3-8-102. A. As used in the Terry Peach North Canadian
22 Watershed Water Restoration Act:
23 1. “Commission” means the Oklahoma Conservation Commission;
24
